<div id="donate-modal" 
     class="modal fade" 
     tabindex="-1" 
     role="dialog">
  <div class="modal-dialog <%- isMobile ? 'modal-fullscreen' : '' %>"
       role="document">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header bg-primary">
        <h4 class="modal-title">Enjoying ManyTwitch?</h4>
        <button type="button" 
                class="close btn btn-danger"
                data-bs-dismiss="modal" 
                aria-label="Close"
                title="Close">
          <span aria-hidden="true">
            <i class="fa fa-close"></i>
          </span>
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p>I built ManyTwitch because I wanted to be able to watch my favorite creators on Twitch at the same time. It has become a daily part of my Twitch experience. If you enjoy using this app, please consider donating a dollar or two to help keep it running. ManyTwitch will always be free, will never feature ads and will never collect information about you or who you watch. Thanks for visiting and I hope you enjoy!</p>
        <p class="text-center strong">Click below to support ManyTwitch!</p>
        <div class="d-grid gap-2">
          <a href="https://ko-fi.com/antillian"
             title="Donate to ManyTwitch! (Opens a new tab)"
             class="btn btn-lg btn-success"
             target="_blank">
             Donate!&nbsp;<i class="fa fa-heart"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>